    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Marti Gradivo quem aput <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionem</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiam</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>tempore quo ad eradendum nomen <lb n="3"/>saevissimae dominationis <lb n="4"/>missus cum vexillationes <lb n="5"/>Moesiae inferioris voltus <expan><abbr>hh</abbr><ex>ostium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pp</abbr><ex>ublicorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">de vexillis et can</supplied>tabris <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">ultro detra</supplied>here nollent <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">auctores im</supplied>prosperi conatus <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">coercerat</supplied> congressione <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">facta prima</supplied> in acie constitutus <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">invocave</supplied>rat Clodius Celsinus <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">signum quod in be</supplied>llo voverat <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low"> posuit</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ergänzungen nach Kovács. (B): abweichende Ergänzungen. Datierung: vermutlich 238 (mit dem Tod von Maximinus Thrax) oder 249 n. Chr. (Regierungsantritt von Decius).</p>
            </div>
